title: 2020-01-13 - TAFOF Unpacker
plain_text:
# TAFOF Unpacker

**github.com/Tera0017/TAFOF-Unpacker**

Tera0017

### TA505 Unpacker is a python 2.7 script that is able to unpack statically, x86 and x64 TA505 packed samples.

 Currently malware spotted to be packed with that packer:

 GetandGoDll Silence (https://twitter.com/Vishnyak0v/status/1199620846823890944) TinyMet (https://twitter.com/darb0ng/status/1202823405747073024) Azorult (https://twitter.com/Vishnyak0v/status/1204312402306752513) KBMiner (https://www.botconf.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/B2019- Eremin_Bot_with_rootkit.pdf) ...
